  "title": "Forklift Driver",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Follow instructions of the Supervisor and ensure that forklift is handled and driven in a proper manner</li>\n  <li>Loading &amp; unloading goods in container and lorry</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper label on the cargo in and out</li>\n  <li>Picking / packing and receiving</li>\n  <li>Carry up to 5kg per carton</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned by superior</li>\n  <li>Can drive reach truck</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>O-Level / N-Level / NITEC Holder</li>\n  <li>Valid forklift licence required</li>\n  <li>Min. 2 years' experience in warehouse</li>\n  <li>Physically fit</li>\n  <li>Friendly, co-operative and good team player</li>\n  <li>Outgoing and team orientated personality</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills: spoken and written English</li>\n  <li>5.5 days work week</li>\n  <li>Must be willing to work OT including Public Holidays</li>\n</ul>",
